Marie Alice Johnson, by Clarence E. Johnson, appellant, v. Emil Hanson, appellee.Gen. No. 31,924.

Heard in the third division of this court for the first district at the March term, 1927.

Opinion filed January 18, 1928.Kirkland, Patterson & Fleming, for appellant; Howard Ellis and William H. Symmes., of counsel.Joseph H. Hinshaw, for appellee; Oswell G. Treadway, of counsel. Mr. Justice Holdom

delivered the opinion of the court.
